videos.description: Rudy Gobert goes up for the dunk, but Jarrett Allen meets him there with the block to set up Taurean Prince's 3-pointer at the other end.

videos.description: Jarrett Allen says he owes his 19-point, 18-rebound night to a switch from pesto to Alfredo sauce on his pregame pasta.
